==Ancient Greek==

===Etymology===
Middle voice from [[χάρις]] {{GG|5485}}

===Pronunciation===
χαρίζομαι / charizomai / khar-id'-zom-ahee

===Verb===
'''χαρίζομαι'''

# to [[grant]] as a favor, that is, gratuitously, in kindness, pardon or rescue: - [[deliver]], (frankly) [[forgive]], (freely) give, [[grant]].

